
"How to use git to maintain your code

update your project
1. git init (it is necessary when you push your project first )

2. git add file1 file2 file3... or git add . //git add . means add all files

3. git commit -m "comment" 

4. git remote add origin

5. git pull origin master / git pull origin master --allow-unrelated-histories    //it's good for you to keep your project complete 

6. git push (-u) origin master  // you need add -u when you push your project the first time
